description: LIUM wishes to eliminate unnecessary intermediaries to guarantee safe, accurate and cost friendly transactions. Essential services and technology as accurate information of service and produce, quick transaction, super smart contract, payment service, and escrow service will also be provided. Also, low commission fee that only occurs for successful transactions will contribute to increasing the quality of the products and services. Through super smart contract, all transactions occurring through mobile and PC interface are automatically recorded and stored in the blocks.
